Chess/PGN/EPD version 0.19
==========================

CHESS::PGN::EPD - Perl extension to produce and manipulate EPD text.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DOCUMENTATION

Available using various Pod Mods(tm) from source: epd.pm.

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

Chess::PGN::Moves
Chess::PGN::Parse (useless without, not actually required though...)
DB_File
Test
Text::CSV


